{"tid":760454,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[輕小說/漫畫][推廣] 不過是蜘蛛甚麼的/我係蜘蛛，唔得呀?","createTime":"2018-07-29T14:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T05:19:47.000Z","uid":54437,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c37d89116acc0e781991685f06a37a9ee89b6f1c","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"**麻煩盡量唔好劇透，或者用細字講**<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/220323_cb9471bc2ac2a244cd21eb64ff9afe35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F220323_cb9471bc2ac2a244cd21eb64ff9afe35.jpg&h=546cfa9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/220319_53189e00fb82af1d6135b8ac248bd3e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F220319_53189e00fb82af1d6135b8ac248bd3e7.jpg&h=2b93a8ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己由漫畫入坑，覺得好好睇<br />\n極速追晒漫畫，之後文庫版，最後追埋web版 (之後會再講有乜分別)<br />\n<br />\n所以決定開個post推廣下<br />\n唔知呢度有幾多人睇，為左唔好劇透希望大家小心啲，如果真係好多人想傾可能開多個post講劇情<br />\n===================<br />\n簡介：<br />\n某日，日本高中某班級&ldquo;唔知點解&ldquo;爆炸，全個班嘅人都炸死左， &ldquo;唔知點解&ldquo;轉生左去某個異世界。<br />\n咁女主角都喺個班房，一樣炸死左轉生，但係 &ldquo;唔知點解&ldquo;轉左做隻蜘蛛魔物，仲要係嗰個世界魔物入面差唔多最廢嘅。主角(通稱蜘蛛子)一出世就要為生存奮戰&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有咩好睇：<br />\n1. 戰鬥(戰術)<br />\n<br />\n蜘蛛子轉生做嘅魔物雖然廢，但係都有特長：絲同毒。<br />\n加上蜘蛛子嘅智慧，不斷靠各種神戰術同計策，打敗各種本應贏唔到嘅對手。<br />\n<br />\n有啲hunter用腦戰鬥嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n2. 伏筆 (呢點漫畫版暫時唔多適用，之後會講)<br />\n<br />\n上面所有 &ldquo;唔知點解&ldquo; 其實後來都會有解釋。唔係為兜而兜，夾硬解釋，而係作者一早設定好晒，仲好用心咁隱藏部分重點，亦會加上適量伏筆/疑點，等觀眾可以一路睇一路估。<br />\n<br />\n當然，你都可以放棄思考，直接等劇情開估。就算係咁，到開完估，你知道多左之後，用另一個角度諗返/睇返之前嘅劇情就會有另一返風味。<br />\n<br />\n3. 搞笑 / 多neta<br />\n<br />\n因為蜘蛛子本身嘅性格 (懶好笑自言自語，吐槽，成日得意忘形), 另到本來嚴肅嘅劇情間唔中會爆出笑點。漫畫仲加上埋可愛嘅畫風，另成件事多左份喜感。<br />\n<br />\n=================<br />\n之後再講下各個版本嘅分別<br />\n(待續&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"b46be0848e84438ee72fda2201301a1d6f60329d","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:21:39.000Z","msg":"上面提過有幾個版本<br />\n一開始係web小說黎，web版依家仲連載緊<br />\n之後hit左就改編左出書(文庫版)同漫畫<br />\n仲好似話動畫化緊<br />\n<br />\n唔同版本劇情上(暫時)唔大分別<br />\n不過個敘事方法就差好遠<br />\n=============<br />\n漫畫(暫時)只係以蜘蛛子視點去畫，冇轉過視點，冇乜提過其他轉生者<br />\n<br />\n而文字版就會間唔中轉下視點，等觀眾可以由唔同角度了解個世界又或者係劇情<br />\n<br />\n上面提過，個人幾鍾意嘅多伏筆/估劇情，部分就係靠轉視點造出黎<br />\n<br />\n所以如果因為鍾意漫畫而走去搵小說黎睇就未必會有興趣"},{"pid":"722cd592ebf338407f4c0d4bed4bde25969cd7cf","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"漫畫過癮好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa547d35ac1838c0cac18bc5a5620363a8007f78","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"722cd592ebf338407f4c0d4bed4bde25969cd7cf","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"漫畫過癮好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:10:35.000Z","msg":"竟然有人"},{"pid":"d1591e65292d1f96d5b00b97ac4bb1e8b8ceeed2","tid":760454,"uid":32606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"hi 底巴我都有睇漫畫版，諗住遲啲睇埋小說版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4342318333aa238cb1693499620e34ed7d29472f","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"722cd592ebf338407f4c0d4bed4bde25969cd7cf","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"漫畫過癮好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"漫畫同小說直係完全2回事黎<br />\n睇你鍾意 輕鬆明快 定 輕鬆得黎有啲縣疑(？)<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢畫啲人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到蜘蛛子離開左迷宮之後都唔知點算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋之後唔知佢會點，keep住由蜘蛛子順住畫落去"},{"pid":"b341667f9bc61038d730a9cb7bf8e94d75a8461b","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1591e65292d1f96d5b00b97ac4bb1e8b8ceeed2","tid":760454,"uid":32606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"hi 底巴我都有睇漫畫版，諗住遲啲睇埋小說版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:21:30.000Z","msg":"Kr人又攻佔啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2452206b575b44fe08b16103263425a8f9b106bd","tid":760454,"uid":93752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"蜘蛛子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b600dfe4ad7cc408afe54ccc7aca268e777d6350","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4342318333aa238cb1693499620e34ed7d29472f","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"722cd592ebf338407f4c0d4bed4bde25969cd7cf","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"漫畫過癮好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"漫畫同小說直係完全2回事黎<br />\n睇你鍾意 輕鬆明快 定 輕鬆得黎有啲縣疑(？)<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢畫啲人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到蜘蛛子離開左迷宮之後都唔知點算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋之後唔知佢會點，keep住由蜘蛛子順住畫落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"小說睇左半卷 覺得尚算OK 但嫌推進慢得濟<br />\n漫畫就畫風+表情+對白 偏輕鬆 我當日常睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我想知佢後面有咩懸疑 <br />\n巴打可唔可以用幾句講小小黎聽下 唔洗講曬"},{"pid":"b586e363db3e9bd40e63c1ffc63f68e0de0e0d09","tid":760454,"uid":68569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"漫畫fans here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2174477def87cf9d26bc3174381d733ae0227211","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b600dfe4ad7cc408afe54ccc7aca268e777d6350","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4342318333aa238cb1693499620e34ed7d29472f","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"722cd592ebf338407f4c0d4bed4bde25969cd7cf","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"漫畫過癮好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"漫畫同小說直係完全2回事黎<br />\n睇你鍾意 輕鬆明快 定 輕鬆得黎有啲縣疑(？)<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢畫啲人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到蜘蛛子離開左迷宮之後都唔知點算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋之後唔知佢會點，keep住由蜘蛛子順住畫落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"小說睇左半卷 覺得尚算OK 但嫌推進慢得濟<br />\n漫畫就畫風+表情+對白 偏輕鬆 我當日常睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我想知佢後面有咩懸疑 <br />\n巴打可唔可以用幾句講小小黎聽下 唔洗講曬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"其實又冇懸疑咁誇張<br />\n見我上面都打左個問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如估下啲角色轉生前係邊個啊<br />\n蜘蛛子開打前懶有型咁話有戰術，估下佢個策略係點啊<br />\n估下事件背後邊個係黑手啊<br />\n<br />\n其實主要都係由唔同人視點去講同一件事<br />\n等讀者可以&quot;砌埋&quot;啲資訊，或者發現到啲矛盾位，知道/估到事件嘅全貌<br />\n<br />\n除左爆點，有時都會帶黎啲笑點<br />\n例如蜘蛛子視點求其做左啲好膠嘅野<br />\n但係另一個角色就好認真咁去分析蜘蛛子嘅深意，最後得出蜘蛛子好恐怖嘅結論"},{"pid":"428c20150261bfd831689ca37c805629ff333f95","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2174477def87cf9d26bc3174381d733ae0227211","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b600dfe4ad7cc408afe54ccc7aca268e777d6350","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4342318333aa238cb1693499620e34ed7d29472f","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"漫畫同小說直係完全2回事黎<br />\n睇你鍾意 輕鬆明快 定 輕鬆得黎有啲縣疑(？)<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢畫啲人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到蜘蛛子離開左迷宮之後都唔知點算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋之後唔知佢會點，keep住由蜘蛛子順住畫落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"小說睇左半卷 覺得尚算OK 但嫌推進慢得濟<br />\n漫畫就畫風+表情+對白 偏輕鬆 我當日常睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我想知佢後面有咩懸疑 <br />\n巴打可唔可以用幾句講小小黎聽下 唔洗講曬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"其實又冇懸疑咁誇張<br />\n見我上面都打左個問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如估下啲角色轉生前係邊個啊<br />\n蜘蛛子開打前懶有型咁話有戰術，估下佢個策略係點啊<br />\n估下事件背後邊個係黑手啊<br />\n<br />\n其實主要都係由唔同人視點去講同一件事<br />\n等讀者可以&quot;砌埋&quot;啲資訊，或者發現到啲矛盾位，知道/估到事件嘅全貌<br />\n<br />\n除左爆點，有時都會帶黎啲笑點<br />\n例如蜘蛛子視點求其做左啲好膠嘅野<br />\n但係另一個角色就好認真咁去分析蜘蛛子嘅深意，最後得出蜘蛛子好恐怖嘅結論"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"有啲位擺明係作者突登砌出黎<br />\n<br />\n例如整段2個人嘅對話，又唔開名，等你唔知係邊個同邊個講<br />\n<br />\n咁順住睇睇下你可能會留意到啲key word, 就會醒返起段對話，心諗唔通係A同B講野？<br />\n<br />\n到作者劇情入面開估，講返其實係A同C<br />\n仲解釋返原來一早有伏筆提過冇可能係B，只係你自己諗漏左"},{"pid":"069cfe62c80a57def2e9dba4c4c35154a521d316","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"428c20150261bfd831689ca37c805629ff333f95","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2174477def87cf9d26bc3174381d733ae0227211","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b600dfe4ad7cc408afe54ccc7aca268e777d6350","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"小說睇左半卷 覺得尚算OK 但嫌推進慢得濟<br />\n漫畫就畫風+表情+對白 偏輕鬆 我當日常睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我想知佢後面有咩懸疑 <br />\n巴打可唔可以用幾句講小小黎聽下 唔洗講曬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"其實又冇懸疑咁誇張<br />\n見我上面都打左個問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如估下啲角色轉生前係邊個啊<br />\n蜘蛛子開打前懶有型咁話有戰術，估下佢個策略係點啊<br />\n估下事件背後邊個係黑手啊<br />\n<br />\n其實主要都係由唔同人視點去講同一件事<br />\n等讀者可以&quot;砌埋&quot;啲資訊，或者發現到啲矛盾位，知道/估到事件嘅全貌<br />\n<br />\n除左爆點，有時都會帶黎啲笑點<br />\n例如蜘蛛子視點求其做左啲好膠嘅野<br />\n但係另一個角色就好認真咁去分析蜘蛛子嘅深意，最後得出蜘蛛子好恐怖嘅結論"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"有啲位擺明係作者突登砌出黎<br />\n<br />\n例如整段2個人嘅對話，又唔開名，等你唔知係邊個同邊個講<br />\n<br />\n咁順住睇睇下你可能會留意到啲key word, 就會醒返起段對話，心諗唔通係A同B講野？<br />\n<br />\n到作者劇情入面開估，講返其實係A同C<br />\n仲解釋返原來一早有伏筆提過冇可能係B，只係你自己諗漏左"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"呢種唔開名對話方式 好多小説都有用<br />\nbtw我以為呢套會好似史萊姆咁後期玩到變埋人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8621baa37421bc551dd37b7ebae83006841f423","tid":760454,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"負皮係比垃圾名 = =<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/011013_08a8fdf913818458958d911d96726988.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F011013_08a8fdf913818458958d911d96726988.png&h=ff6b8bf5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec9964af9401b7a822ba6aab24109bd487661929","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8621baa37421bc551dd37b7ebae83006841f423","tid":760454,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"負皮係比垃圾名 = =<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/011013_08a8fdf913818458958d911d96726988.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F011013_08a8fdf913818458958d911d96726988.png&h=ff6b8bf5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:20:45.000Z","msg":"Sorry<br />\n冇google到邊個先係正式名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94530c71612d08374c9a8165bcc8d3bf2c333e0a","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"069cfe62c80a57def2e9dba4c4c35154a521d316","tid":760454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"428c20150261bfd831689ca37c805629ff333f95","tid":760454,"uid":54437,