,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:28:02.000Z","msg":"同埋有d位怪怪地<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">白竟然揀唔去偷聽教王開會<br />\n另外有個位做左d望落冇咁著數o既選擇 (呢個唔記得詳情)<br />\n<br />\n有可能係白發覺佢主觀角度畀人(D?黑?)監視緊<br />\n有d野大約估到就算，如果親眼去確認就會畀人知道埋咁</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實用咩色先最難睇到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a973f2f5778cadbaefaf598343ad0419504a907","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee147835282caa33f156b52d078182a00292e279","tid":760454,"uid":82028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:57:20.000Z","msg":"我想知佢滿lv左個禁忌知道左咩啲會咁嬲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"世界o既真理 (無誤<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.webqxs.com/0/13/6381.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.webqxs.com%2F0%2F13%2F6381.html&d=BVLY2Jx7JIkSF0MxOOUexv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9dc0b2bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.webqxs.com/0/13/6381.html</a><br />\n其實都講到幾白，不過只係講左結論(知道左之後蜘蛛子想做乜) 冇講原因<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">大約係個世界o既歷史，點解會有技能系統之類<br />\n<br />\n表面上係D救左班轉生者，但係睇完就覺得D係放佢地上&quot;木台&quot;，想佢地o係個世界做d野<br />\n又或者係D想睇佢地知道左個世界o既情況之後會點做<br />\n<br />\n講到呢度應該都唔係透左好多野<br />\n你想可以再講深入d，不過之後睇到就會少左d樂趣<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"fb1c1db747876e03eed4969d3d3ad94739e4ff72","tid":760454,"uid":82028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a973f2f5778cadbaefaf598343ad0419504a907","tid":760454,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee147835282caa33f156b52d078182a00292e279","tid":760454,"uid":82028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:57:20.000Z","msg":"我想知佢滿lv左個禁忌知道左咩啲會咁嬲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"世界o既真理 (無誤<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.webqxs.com/0/13/6381.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.webqxs.com%2F0%2F13%2F6381.html&d=BV